01.Name: Nike jordan
01.description: The Air Jordan 1 Retro High OG 'Chicago' 2022 is a reissue of the original 'Chicago' colorway that Michael Jordan wore during his rookie season with the Chicago Bulls. The shoe's upper is built with a blend of leather and synthetic, finished in a mix of white, black and Varsity Red. The high-top rides on a classic Air midsole, supported underfoot by a concentric rubber outsole.
